Fred Testot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Testot 0 Fredéric Giacomo Testot (born 20 February 1977) is a French actor, comedian and filmmaker. He collaborated extensively with Omar Sy on the Canal+ television show Service après-vente des émissions from 2005 to 2012.
